==German==
===Preposition===
'''über'''

#[[above]], [[over]]
# [[by]], [[via]]; [[through]]
Note: The preposition "&uuml;ber" is used with accusative case if the verb shows movement from one place to another, whereas it is used with dative case if the verb shows location.

